Linear does no postprocessing and is fastest to use.
Reinhardt tonemapper is slower, than linear one.
Filmic tonemapper is slower, than Reinhardt one.
ACES tonemapper is slower, than Filmic one.
AGX tonemapper is relatively new, and is the slowest one."

